{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "安らかな譫言", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-5", "avgTag": "戦闘後", "storyName": "マスカレードへの招待状", "storyInfo": "モーフィアスは、睦の夢が簡単に覚ませるものではないと告げる。夢の中で「睦」は自分の望んだ人生を手に入れており、その夢を守るため、睦を救おうとする祥子を崖から突き落とした。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g6_rmbtmine", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "nrun"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "nrun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁ……はぁ……くっ……！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_airshiptakeoff", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "machine"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "machine", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "machine", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掘削機の重苦しい音が、がらんとした洞窟内に響いている。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "気温は徐々に下がっていく。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洞窟を抜け出した瞬間、冷気が祥子を襲った。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その刺すような寒さに、鼓動がますます早まっていく。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしは……どうやってあの子と向き合えばいいの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何かを伝えることも、顔を合わせることもできない。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "やれやれ、どうすればいいのかしらね。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "振り向かずとも、誰が来たかは明らかだった。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの子の夢、とっても気に入っちゃったわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どんな子にも素敵な夢を見せてあげるのが夢のお城の役目。だからあの子の願いも全部叶えてあげたわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうしたら、意外と安定してる――ううん、それどころか、この夢は完璧よ。まさかここまで上手くいくなんて。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに今は、もっと面白いことになってるしね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……睦を騙していますのね。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "騙す？　そんなことするわけないじゃない。何度も交渉して、あの子も私の正体はよく知ってるもの。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最高の結果になって、とっても嬉しいわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢だと理解していながら、それでもここを離れたくない。それってつまり、私の夢作りが完璧って証拠よね？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1937_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_yingying_ked_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（賛成するような鳴き声）", "name": "カールトンたち"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1937_1#3$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あら？　あんたが来るなんて……", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふふっ、面白いわね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私はここで失礼するわ。祥子、あんたもすぐこの夢の面白さに気付くはずよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shdwblwvr", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃん、みんな待ってる。帰ろう？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どこへ帰ると言うんですの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "モーフィアスが消えても、少しも驚きませんのね……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここにあるものは、全部私たちが作った「ウソ」だから。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「私たち」……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたは……私たちのものじゃない。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g9_warmrabbitnest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electricguitar", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦ちゃんの演奏、本当に良かった〜！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥……", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ねぇ、ママ……祥はどこ？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "さきちゃん？　あれ？　どこに行ったのかしら……", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#6$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "違う……祥は、私を置いて行ったりしない。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#6$3"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賑やかにしていた聴衆が突然静まり、睦に視線を注いだ。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦ちゃん、忘れちゃったみたいね――", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここはあなただけの夢じゃないの。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここは「私たち」の夢。", "name": "「睦の母」"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「私たち」。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この夢の中では、すべての「睦」が願いを叶えられる。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私たちは睦ちゃんを中心に、私たちだけの美しい夢を作った。みんなが幸せになれる、そんな夢をね。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私たちは睦ちゃんの中から、ずっとその人生を見てきた。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それで、最後はみんなの意見が一致したんだ。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃんは、私たちの敵だって。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦、何を言っていますの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしも、あなたにこれ以上辛い思いはさせたくありません。でも、こんな夢に逃げていてはいけないのです。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "違う！　大事なのは、睦ちゃんがここでずっと幸せでいることだもん！", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だから祥子ちゃん、私の言うことを聞いて。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここに残って、一緒に睦ちゃんの夢を守ろうよ。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦ちゃんは弱い子だから、迷ってるんだ。目を覚ましたほうがいいか、このまま幸せな夢を見続けるかって。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今の睦ちゃんにとっては、祥子ちゃんだけが現実かどうかの基準なんだよ。だから祥子ちゃんのいる場所が「現実」になるの。", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃんが残ってくれたら、この夢を一生見ていられる。それってもう「現実」とほとんど変わらないでしょ？", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だから祥子ちゃん、ここに残ろう？", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お断りします。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……残ってくれないの？", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現実の睦は、今もあの冷たい夢のお城で眠っていますわ。そんな結末でいいと本気で思ってますの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本当に睦を愛しているなら、こんなことはできないはずですわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦ちゃんが幸せでいられるなら、私たちみんなが生きていられるなら――そこが本当の現実かどうかなんて、どうだっていい！", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私は睦ちゃんの記憶を全部持ってる。だから、祥子ちゃんの本当の望みも知ってるんだよ！？", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃんがここに残ってくれたら、完璧なAve{@nbs}Mujicaだって実現してあげられるよ！", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#7$3"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "やめなさい！　あなたは睦ではありません。睦はそんなことを言ったりしませんわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#11$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんな……祥子ちゃんも、睦ちゃんも大好きなのに……", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#11$3"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうして私を板挟みにするの？", "name": "「睦」"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#11$3"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「殺れ。」", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "at